### ============================================
### 用户模块接口测试
### ============================================

### 1. 注册 — 成功
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "teacher",
  "realName": "张老师",
  "email": "teacher@qq.com"
}

###

### 2. 注册 — 重复用户名（应返回"用户名已存在"）
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "teacher",
  "realName": "张老师",
  "email": "teacher@qq.com"
}

###

### 3. 注册 — 学生账号
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "student",
  "realName": "李同学",
  "email": "student@qq.com"
}

###

### 4. 登录 — 成功（复制返回的 token）
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher1",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 5. 登录 — 密码错误
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher1",
  "password": "wrong"
}

###

### 6. 获取用户信息 — 已登录（把 token 替换成第4步返回的值）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIzIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ0ZWFjaGVyMSIsInJvbGUiOiJ0ZWFjaGVyIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMDcxNjkzLCJleHAiOjE3ODMxNTgwOTN9.w1oj5_PSEnXyWZBEyHrFwPTpfFAEsTl9v0LPf58dtN8

###

### 7. 获取用户信息 — 未登录（应返回 401）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/info

###

### 8. 测试接口 — 无需登录
GET http://localhost:8080/test
